prompts.frontCover: Minimalist greeting card front, clean flat 2D illustration. A cartoon version of Jordan from the reference photo, wearing a dark blue t-shirt, is depicted as a snowboarder comically sliding down a giant, perfectly marbled slice of Wagyu steak as if it were a snowy mountain slope. He has a wide, happy grin and is holding onto a pair of oversized chopsticks instead of ski poles. Cartoon Lao Lao from the photo, wearing a white zip-up jacket, stands at the bottom of the "steak slope" with a warm, amused smile, ready to catch him. Floating around them are minimalist, icon-style illustrations: a single piece of salmon nigiri sushi, a stylized Chinese takeout box, and a laptop with simple lines of code on the screen `< >`. The background is a solid, soft neutral color with plenty of negative space. Centered in the middle of the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Jordan".
